  <!-- ========== 08. TEXT CONVENTIONS ========== -->
  <div class="g-section">
    <div class="g-kicker">08 · text conventions</div>
    <div class="g-title">voice + syntax</div>
    <div class="g-desc">
      The writing style is part of the brand. Code-flavored, terse, lowercase. Comments use // prefix. Labels use dot.notation and bracket[syntax].
    </div>

    <div class="code">
      <span class="comment">/* Text patterns used throughout */</span><br><br>
      // good morning, tg<br>
      [<b>section</b>] context.label · src: tool<br>
      year.progress · q2 · day 104 of 365 · 28%<br>
      // non-negotiable. sets the day.<br>
      compiled 06:00 ct<br>
      // discipline = freedom<br><br>
      <span class="comment">/* Separator: centered dot ( · ) */</span><br>
      apr 14, 2026 · anthropic · 3 min read<br><br>
      <span class="comment">/* Never use: em-dashes, Title Case, exclamation marks, emoji */</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ========== 09. MOBILE ========== -->
  <div class="g-section">
    <div class="g-kicker">09 · responsive</div>
    <div class="g-title">mobile behavior</div>
    <div class="g-desc">
      Everything collapses gracefully. No hamburger menus, no hidden content. Content reflows, type scales down, grids stack.
    </div>

    <div class="code">
      <span class="comment">/* Breakpoints */</span><br><br>
      @media (max-width: 820px)<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;signal cards: 3-col → 1-col stack<br><br>
      @media (max-width: 720px)<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;2-column layouts collapse<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;pillars grid: 2x2 → 1-col<br><br>
      @media (max-width: 640px)<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;body: 13px (from 13.5px)<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;hero h1: 21px (from 26px)<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;page padding: 28px 16px 80px<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;stat grid: 4-up → 2-up<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;finance grid: 4-up → 2-up<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;section header .rule: hidden<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;buttons: full-width stacked<br>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;event blocks: stack vertical
    </div>
  </div>

